  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to identify phenotypic groups of patients with periodontitis by applying a
      cluster analysis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a retrospective cross-sectional study based on a prospectively maintained database of
      consecutive patients attending the Departement of Periodontology at the Rothschild hospital.
      A cluster analysis will help to distinguish clinical and microbiological profils of
      periodontal patients.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
